payload.prompt: Close-up on Rick Sanchez from Rick and Morty. He’s swaying slightly, flask in hand, drool on his lip, eyes bloodshot but full of manic energy. The background suggests absurdly huge giants looming, but they’re out of focus — only their massive buttcheeks are visible behind him, blurred and ridiculous. Rick is front and center, ranting and gesturing wildly, pointing back over his shoulder with mocking disbelief. His mouth movements are exaggerated, full of drunken burps and sarcastic sneers, as he lays into the giants with his trademark cynical tone. The scene feels chaotic, fast-talking, and unhinged, but the focus stays tightly on Rick’s face, expressions, and drunken mannerisms.
